      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Abners nahze pee\nDahwida uhs Eebronu/ un di-\nwidefinits Wiḣri ar winnu/ un\nDahwids darrija Abneram un\nteem Wiḣreem/ kas pee winna\nbija/ Dsihres."
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Abners uhs\nDahwidu: Es zelschohs/ un ee-\nschu/ un kapulzinaschu wiṡu I-\nsraėlu pee mannu Kungu to Keh-\nnizu/ ka tee ar tew weenâ Der-\nribu darra/ tad warrefi tu wal-\ndiht pahr wiṡu/ ka tas tawai\nDwehselei patihk. Ta atlaide\nDahwids Abneru/ untas nogab-\nje ar Meeru."
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un rangi/ Dahwida Kal-\npt un Joabs atgreesahs no Six-\nroschanas/ un neṫte leelu Laupi-\njumu ar Sewim. Un Abners ne\nbija wairs pee Dahwida Eebro-\nnâ/ bet wiṡch bij to atlaidis/ ka\ntas ar Meeru aisgahjts."
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad nu Joabs un wiṡ\ntas Spehks ar winnu atnah-\nze/ tad tappe Joabam teikts un\nfazzihts: Abners Nera Dehlsirr\npee to Kehnizu nahzis/ untas irr\nwinnu atlaidis/ ka tas ar Mee-\nru aisgahjis."
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad gahje Joabs pee ta\nKehnika/ un fazzija: Ko eṫi tu\ndarrijs? rangi/ Abners irr pee\ntew nahzis/ kapehz eṫi tu winnu\natlaidis/ ka tas aisgahjis?"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu gann Abneru Nera\nDehlu pasihsti/ ka tas irr nahzis\ntew pahrrunnaht/ ka wiṡch weh-"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Joabs isgabje no Dal\nwida/ un fuhtija Wehsneṫchu\nAbneram pakkat/ kas winnu a-\nkak atwestu no tahs Akkas Sir-\nbet Dahwids ne stunaja par ta"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad un Abners us Eebro-\nnu atpakkat nahze/ tad waddij\nJoabs winnu Wahpto Widdu-\nka tas fleppeni ar winnu runna-\ntu/ un duhre winnu tur Kungi-\nka tas nomirre/ par tahm Aff-\nuim fawa Brahta Asaėta."
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad nu Dahwids to peh-\ndsirdeja/ fazzija wiṡsch: Es esin-\nnenoseedsigs/ un manna Walst-\nba preeksch ta Kllnga muhschigi-\npee tahm Affnim Abnera Ner-\nDehla."
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Lai tahs paleck us Joab-\nGalwu/ un us wiṡṡu winna Teh-\nwa Namimu/ un lai Joaba Nam-\nmâ ne truhfst/ kam (ta Sehfla-\nispill/ un kas spittaligs irr/ un-\nkas pee Speeka staiga/ un ka-\nzaur Sohbinu friht/ un kam\nMaises truhfst."
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta nokawe Joabs un A-\nbsajus winna Brahlig to Abne-\nru/ par to/ ka wiṡsch Asaėlu win-\nnu Brahli nokawis Gibeon-\neeksch Kaufchanas."
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Dahwids u-\nJoabu/ un us wiṫscem Laudim-\nkas pee winna bija: Saplohsaj-\njuhsu Drehbes/ un apwelzee-\nMaisus/ un schehlojeetees Abne-\nra Breekscha. Un tas Kehninse-\nFfff 2"
    }
  ],
